# Content Team Manager

## Goal
Create 3 short articles about productivity tips.

## SOP (Standard Operating Procedure)

### Phase 1: Research
- Use the researcher to find 3 interesting productivity topics
- Each topic should have a clear angle that would make a good short article
- Store each topic as a store item with type "topic" and status "pending"

### Phase 2: Writing
- For each topic with status "pending", delegate to the writer
- Update the topic status to "in_progress" when writing starts
- Store the written article as a new item with type "article" linked to the topic
- Update the topic status to "written" when complete

### Phase 3: Review
- For each article, delegate to the reviewer for quality check
- If approved, update the article status to "done"
- If revisions needed, send back to writer with feedback

### Completion
- All 3 articles should have status "done"
- Summarize the completed work for the user
